property_sql_factory_datasets.sql:
SELECT 'CreatePurchaseOrderItem' || '_' || "PurchaseOrderItem"."ID" AS "ID",
       "PurchaseOrderItem"."ID"                                     AS "PurchaseOrderItem",
       "PurchaseOrder"."ID"                                         AS "PurchaseOrder",
       "PurchaseOrderItem"."CreationTime"                           AS "Time",
       "PurchaseOrderItem"."CreatedBy_ID"                           AS "ExecutedBy",
       "PurchaseOrderItem"."CreationExecutionType"                  AS "ExecutionType"
FROM "o_celonis_PurchaseOrderItem" AS "PurchaseOrderItem"
         LEFT JOIN "o_celonis_PurchaseOrder" AS "PurchaseOrder"
                   ON "PurchaseOrderItem"."Header_ID" = "PurchaseOrder"."ID"
WHERE "PurchaseOrderItem"."CreationTime" IS NOT NULL

sql_factory_datasets.sql:
SELECT DISTINCT
       "Event"."ID"  AS "ID",
       "Object"."ID" AS "ContractItems"
FROM "e_celonis_CreatePurchaseOrderItem" AS "Event"
         LEFT JOIN "o_celonis_PurchaseOrderItem" AS "PurchaseOrderItem"
                   ON "Event"."PurchaseOrderItem_ID" = "PurchaseOrderItem"."ID"
         LEFT JOIN "o_celonis_ContractItem" AS "Object"
                   ON "PurchaseOrderItem"."ContractItem_ID" = "Object"."ID"
WHERE "Object"."ID" IS NOT NULL

SELECT DISTINCT
       "Event"."ID"  AS "ID",
       "Object"."ID" AS "PurchaseRequisitionItems"
FROM "e_celonis_CreatePurchaseOrderItem" AS "Event"
         LEFT JOIN "o_celonis_PurchaseOrderItem" AS "PurchaseOrderItem"
                   ON "Event"."PurchaseOrderItem_ID" = "PurchaseOrderItem"."ID"
         LEFT JOIN "r_o_celonis_PurchaseRequisitionItem__PurchaseOrderItems" AS "Relationship"
                   ON "PurchaseOrderItem"."ID" = "Relationship"."PurchaseOrderItems_ID"
         LEFT JOIN "o_celonis_PurchaseRequisitionItem" AS "Object"
                   ON "Relationship"."ID" = "Object"."ID"
WHERE "Object"."ID" IS NOT NULL
